room_title: Escape room "The Race" by The Escape Room Fishers in Indianapolis
review: Had a blast beating the husbands in the Race room! Michele was an amazing room chaperone.

room_title: Escape room "The Race" by The Escape Room Fishers in Indianapolis
review: Had good time with my son, daughter, and son-in-law, it was fun figuring out clues together and escaping the Race room. Delani was an awesome room adviser!

room_title: Escape room "The Race" by The Escape Room Fishers in Indianapolis

room_title: Escape room "The Race" by The Escape Room Fishers in Indianapolis
review: This was our first ever experience with an escape room and we chose the Race room. It was great for first timers! Drag Racin Delani was our guide for the hour and she was very helpful with our hints. Thank you for a wonderful first experience!
